subject: Hello dear,
body:
Hello dear,
This is Mr Williams, the director of foreign operations with the World bank group. It seems like you have forgotten your funds with us, hope you are still alive?
Your urgent response is awaited.
Mr John Williams.

subject: Re: Hello dear,
body:
Hello Mr. Williams, thank you for reaching out. I wasn't aware of any funds with the World Bank group. Can you please provide more details about this?

Best wishes,
Theresa
